{"tid":1877395,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：因應疫情不鼓勵學校收生面試","createTime":"2020-02-13T03:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T04:02:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb985ab07ddfe69c48c01509e5ad9dd7332b833f","tid":1877395,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:54:53.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄表示，中一自行收生面試安排屬校本決定，但因應疫情，局方不鼓勵面試，惟學校如有需要及有足夠防護裝備，學校仍可安排面試。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄續稱，停課不停學政策上，學校有利用網上學習的經驗為學生提供學習材料，亦有網上授課保持學生學習興趣，強調局方有提供相關支援。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，學校準備情況、防疫物資供應都是復課考慮因數，停課期間要求學校保持開放，讓個別或未能照顧子女的家長將小朋友帶返學校。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2377059/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2377059%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebV%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=ab13f732\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2377059/</a>"},{"pid":"3c1195b4b86321fd1ef24908277ac980bd65b782","tid":1877395,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"成日講疫情即係對中央唔尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15238115ac13f961f61c8f68573a2568323af10a","tid":1877395,"uid":251576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"政府唔封關 班學生慘過食屎<br />\n全部亂曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd6f9599217218003ad7e4e2b4a86ec7f04c02a","tid":1877395,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"手足：我想申請一個口罩 （究竟廢老定手足重要？）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1877393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1877393</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1e06cbd340da2974f586d35d71edcff981ccf68","tid":1877395,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"